defaultThe culture that ‘’employing women was a complete 
defaultwaste of time, since they will 
defaultget married and leave just as they became useful’’ is still in evidence. This can be coupled with the male perception that ‘’all women behave in the same 
defaultway 
defaultas th
defaulte most air-headed female they know’’.
default&#xa0;defaultWomen are the child-bearers and parenthood can bring with it career limitations relating to the ability to travel abroad for work and less capacity to work long hours to meet impending
default deadlines, due to caring  commitments. Th
defaultis can compromise both work and
