defaultWomen can feel their career has stagnated since having children and can also feel 
defaultthat 
defaultbecoming a parent has put up 
defaultfurther barriers to promotion based on the demands of the next career steps, e.g. international recognition if travel has been restricted. T
defaulthis can be seen as impacting on visibility and ultimately career progression which in turn can lead to disillusionment.
